headline: Building Materials Stocks Q4 Recap: Benchmarking Carlisle (NYSE:CSL)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at building materials stocks, starting with Carlisle (NYSE:CSL).
